StatusFinale Categorical variable indicating the final state of the student in the selected year (2018-2019). P1 = Passed in June, P2 = Passed in September, B1 = Failed in June, B2 = Failed in September, NS = Not Scrutinized, T = Transferred, RT = Withdrawn.

Assenze Number of absences updated weekly. Matematica Maths grades average updated weekly. Italiano Italian literature grades average updated weekly. Inglese English grades average updated weekly. NoteMerito Number of notes of merit updated weekly. NoteImpegno Number of notes of diligence updated weekly. NoteDisc Number of disciplinary notes updated weekly. Ritardi Number of delays updated weekly
